channel.title: Running autospawn and .cfg etc
channel.description:
I'm new to everything,I just learned two days ago how to get a server using Hamachi and No-IP. I have 2 questions.
1.How do I open like autospawn and all that stuff. What do I need? It says "Windows can't open this file File: Autospawn.cfg to open this file windows needs to know what program you want to use to open it. Windows can go online and look it up automatically,or you can manually select from a list of programs that are installed on your computer." Then it gives me 2 options what to do,go look for one automatically or select from a list. I downloaded Both JDK update 13,and JRE update 13. They are both on my computer. I have a source I want to edit and everything but I just need to know how to open up the autospawn files and such. Does anyone know my problem?\
2.Do people need to connect to my Hamachi in order to play on my server? It didn't work for my friend unless he downloaded and connected to my Hamachi.
Thanks:) Answer Quick XD
